is widely distributed in the Indian Ocean, Andaman Sea and southern and western Pacific, and is abundant in these regions. Most of the counts characters were overlapped between the western Pacific fish and the Indian Ocean, and Andaman Sea fishes, and some modal differences could found in following characters: pored lateral-line scales 51–62 (vs. 56–64 in Indian Ocean; 52–58 in Andaman Sea;
